name: Raffles Women's Centre - Obstetrics & Gynaecology - 莱佛士妇产科医疗中心

reviews.text: Dr Robin Edwards was simply fantastic. He was informative, thorough and so kind. My daughter was nervous but he put her at ease effortlessly. Between our family of 4 this is the best medical experience we've ever had in Singapore and it is all down to Dr Edwards.

Dr. Aswini Balachandran fails to clearly communicate the costs involved, often leaving patients surprised by unexpected charges at the counter. The lack of transparency comes across as misleading and unprofessional. She’s the worst!
Thank you to Dr Jazlan and the lovely nurses who helped take care of me

Dr Lee I Wen is such a caring and gentle gynae.. she patiently explained every detail to me & provided me options for me to consider. I really appreciate her professionalism. Not forgetting her team of nurses and patient service assistant who is always helpful and warm at every of my visits to Raffles Women centre. Thank you team

Basically you have almost everything you need around here with all the more renowned fashion stores and there's plenty of restaurants for you to choose from. It also house one of the bigger cinema around here.
If you like cheaper food alternatives, there are also plenty around the neighbourhood however you would need to be familar around Punggol to get there.
